data.description: $7000 towards Buyers closing w/acceptable offer .This charming home in SE Huntsville offers a prime location on a spacious lot, creating a serene retreat. The property includes a detached garage for convenience & storage. Inside, the heart of pine floors and rustic beams exude warmth & character, creating an inviting atmosphere. The addition of a new screened-in deck allows for outdoor enjoyment while overlooking a yard adorned w/mature trees. The kitchen features a gas stove, perfect for cooking enthusiasts, w/a cozy fireplace in the great room, ideal for relaxation. Despite its tranquil ambiance, this home is conveniently situated near Jones Valley shopping & dining.
